Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Example 2",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "  Let us define the option price function ",
 StyleBox["V",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " as a ",
 StyleBox["Mathematica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " function that we call OptionValue, and examine some of its \
characteristics.  In addition to current time ",
 StyleBox["t",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
