 ", and riskless rate ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"r", "=", ".04"}], TraditionalForm]]],
 ".  Feel free to run the command several times with this choice of \
parameters, and then to change the parameters to find patterns.  One thing \
that you will always see is that the difference between the stock price and \
the option price is the exercise price at the final time, ",
